        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Building United States Infrastructure and Leveraging Development Act or the BUILD Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases from $15 billion to $30 billion the national limitation on the amount of tax-exempt highway or surface freight transfer facility bonds.</p> <p>The bill also applies the prevailing wage requirements of the Davis-Bacon Act to projects funded by bond issues.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
